<h2>Dataset Description (1.1)</h2>
<p>
  This application uses the <strong>Faker gem</strong> to generate data for three tables:
  <em>Universities</em>, <em>Programs</em>, and <em>Departments</em>.
  Each University has many Programs and many Departments.
</p>

